leagues the organizer of an amateur football tournament in hanoi has had to shortlist and curtail sponsors because there are not enough places for their advertisements which is contrary to professional competitions that cannot find sponsorship the event is officially named hanoi premier league s3 the biggest tournament of grassroots football clubs in northern vietnam s3 refers to the third consecutive annual edition of the hanoi league introducing the s3 on august 19 at press conference in five-star hotel in the capital city vietfootball company the organizer of the league confirmed that tens of sponsors had been denied by the firm they are small sponsors who could commit merely vnd10 million us 455 each in sponsorship the organizer of the competition has never launched a marketing event to advertise the hanoi league according to vietfootball dang ngoc tuan vietfootball's general director said the s3 will be organized from september to november 22 at c500 stadium inside the security institute in hanoi the stadium can welcome around 5,000 people tran huy duc head of the competition unit under the vietnam football federation admitted that the hanoi premier league s3 is the worthiest to watch this time in vietnam the top professional football league of vietnam the v-league has five more weeks to complete its 26 rounds the s3 has the participation of 12 amateur football teams to compete in one-way round robin format every sunday the winning team will get vnd30 million $ 1,360 and the two followers will be awarded vnd20 million and vnd10 million respectively however the biggest prize for players of the teams is the chance and joy of playing pure football amid the applause of thousands of fans on weekends after work tổ chức giải bóng đá nghiệp thầy hiệu trưởng kêu gọi tặng phong bì 20/11 thay hoa quà posted on 21/11/2018 22/11/2018 by thuy thông tin 247 tuần thầy hiệu trưởng thpt anhxtanh hà nội đăng dòng trạng thái kêu gọi tặng phong bì 20/11 thầy quan niệm phong bì lỗi lỗi đa số xác định nghề giáo viên tâm tư tình cảm chả xác định giáo viên giàu nghề giáo viên mắt xã hội trở nên chán nản thương đồng nghiệp vùng cao vất vả lắm thầy đào tuấn tâm sự câu chuyện đằng dòng trạng thái kêu gọi tặng phong bì 20/11 tuần thầy đào tuấn hiệu trưởng trường thpt anhxtanh hà nội đăng tải trang thông điệp đừng tặng hoa đừng tặng quà tặng phong bì nhân 20/11 thầy toàn bộ tiền tặng phong bì 20/11 tiền quỹ dạy hàng lau dọn cửa hàng hát bờ hồ mua chăn tặng thầy cô giáo học sinh trường tiểu học xã pù nhi huyện mường lát tỉnh thanh hóa 19/11 đoàn từ thiện trường thpt anhxtanh hà nội lên đường mường lát tình cảm tập thể giáo viên phụ huynh học sinh mạnh thường quân thầy cô giáo cán bộ công nhân viên học sinh trường tiểu học pù nhi gặp gỡ thầy hiệu trưởng thầy đào tuấn tốt nghiệp đh sư phạm hà nội 1993 thầy giảng viên đh bách khoa hiệu trưởng thpt anhxtanh thầy nhà giáo tinh nghịch đề thi thầy biệt tài 100 học sinh trường tham gia hoạt động thiện nguyện thầy xôn xao dư luận dòng trạng thái kêu gọi tặng phong bì 20/11 mạng xã hội 19/11 hẹn thầy trường nhỏ xinh nằm nép phố thái thịnh đống đa hà nội thầy hiệu trưởng trường thpt anhxtanh cơ ngơi rộng khang trang khuôn viên học sinh thỏa sức vui chơi học tập tâm lý chờ đợi đoàn từ thiện mường lát thầy chút yên tâm thầy đào tuấn sn 1971 hiệu trưởng trường thpt anhxtanh hà nội phong bì lỗi lỗi tặng phong bì vốn nhạy cảm tế nhị ngành giáo dục ngành nghề thầy kêu gọi tặng phong bì nhân 20/11 lầm dư luận tặng phong bì 20/11 tế nhị tranh cãi xã hội món quà vui vẻ món quà món nợ để ý chữ phong bì ngoặc kép phong bì đọc hời hợt lên tiếng chỉ trích giải thích bảo kia làm việc đem tình cảm đồng nghiệp học sinh vùng cao để ý bạn bè quen lối hành văn phong bì quà tặng hai đầu phong bì quan hệ tặng tặng quan điểm thầy tặng phong bì 20/11 tặng tốt đẹp vụ lợi mục đích tặng tiền bạn bè bố mẹ bình thường phong bì vui vui từ chối chả bắt đánh đồng tặng phong bì đút lót mục tiêu phong bì lỗi lỗi giải thích kêu gọi phong bì thầy giáo phụ huynh học sinh tặng phong bì đọc status chém gió kệ sợ sai sai chẳng đấy lắm bạn bè học sinh thế hệ giải thích hộ thầy lầm đa số xác định nghề giáo tâm giáo viên giàu nghề giáo mắt xã hội trở nên chán nản thương đồng nghiệp vùng cao vất vả lắm giải thích mạng xã hội cuộc sống đấy sống hạnh phúc vui vẻ thầy kêu gọi ủng hộ tiền hoạt động thiện nguyện kế hoạch ý tưởng bọn mục tiêu tiền kêu gọi cố gắng tặng chăn ấm học sinh miền núi tặng đầu lẽ chăn quần áo màu sắc hợp văn hóa mặc thoải mái chăn thừa nhà trường phát động phong trào tương tự hưởng ứng hiệu quả chương trình phong trào 20/11 đừng tặng phong bì tặng gạo 2014 bọn phát động phong trào 20/11 đừng tặng phong bì tặng gạo thay gạo bọn gạo hội từ thiện bọn trường thcs tà làng sơn la học sinh nội trú chăn ấm học sinh vùng cao mường lát ảnh fbnv ý nghĩa chương trình quyên góp gạo tặng phong bì 20/11 tặng chăn chẳng qua tiền chăn kêu gọi tặng chăn lung ta lung tung trung chuyển tiền bọn đi mua chăn đồng bộ đẹp gạo bọn tiền thành gạo học sinh gạo trường chính tay múc bát gạo túi nilon gửi gắm tình cảm thư chuyển lên sơn la đơn giản đem bữa cơm ấm tốt đẹp học sinh ý thức hạt gạo quý giá bố mẹ đi kiếm hạt gạo đồng tiền tuần quỹ đoàn từ thiện trường mường lát hành trang mường lát hà nội 250 km 19/11 xe tải chở 656 chăn tặng học sinh thầy trường tiểu học pù nhi bánh anhxtanh trường tiểu học pù nhi tổng cộng trường học sinh chủ yếu dân tộc dao mông mường thái trường học sinh trường 216 pù nhi thầy đồng nghiệp khảo sát địa bàn tình hình kêu gọi tặng phong bì 20/11 bọn đi tiền trạm thay điều tra kĩ qua hội chữ thập đỏ phòng giáo dục tình hình trường học sinh gợi ý chỗ kết nối ban giám hiệu giáo viên miền núi hoàn cảnh không thể nào món quà động viên tinh thần vật chất miền núi lí do nhu cầu tốt nghiệp quản lí hệ thông tin ism demand for information system managers ten years ago was invited to give a seminar about information technology it to the management of a medium-sized company during the visit found that the factory was still using paper report to send information from one group to another asked if there is major problem on the manufacturing assembly line then what will happen a manager told me the worker has to write a report to the supervisor the supervisor must check the problem then writes report to the manufacturing manager the manufacturing manager will contact the engineering department and calls a meeting to report the problem the engineer will write a report to engineer manager and suggests solution to fix the problem the engineer manager will write report to the finance department and ask for a budget to fix the problem the financial manager will write report to the vice president of finance to get approval the vice president approves the budget then writes report to the president about the problem asked how long does it take to reach the decision makers like the vice president ? and how long does it take for the president to know about the problem the answer was on the average it takes about ten days to two weeks because people need time to write report and the report has to be reviewed before it is send to the next level then asked if it takes two weeks to get the problem fixed then what happen to the workers the answer was they have to wait until the problem is fixed because they cannot work when there is problem with the assembly line at that time knew why they had invited me to give a seminar about information technology during the seminar discussed this issue and recommended that they use information technology to increase efficiency and improve performance which received positive respond among managers last year visited the same factory again and found that they had been using an information system to manage the factory assembly lines asked if there is major problem on the assembly line then what will happen this time the answer was about an hour the worker writes report on the computer it system will immediately sends the report to all managers at the same time they have to make decision quickly on how to solve it and at the same time the vice president of finance will approve the budget and the president is informed asked what happen to the workers the answer was they are relocated immediately to another assembly line or other factory works during the fixing time by resources allocation system controlled automatically by the information management systems was impressed after the factory tour went to see the senior managers and praised them for their efforts the senior manager said we are operating in highly competitive environment as medium sized company we are under constant threat from larger companies and if we not change quickly we may be pushed out of business we recognize the importance of managing our factory processes in ways that ensure that our products come to market quickly having the highest quality meet all technical specifications and at good prices the key to this is having good information management strategy as part of our business today businesses are faced with lot of documentation emails and other paperworks and by using an automation system that managed by skilled information system managers we can manage and share information throughout our company the chief information officer explained success involves making long-term plans that are clear and well thought out rather than just reacting to problems when they arise in this business we make a distinction between reactive company and a proactive one the proactive company is the one that plans ahead unfortunately even today many companies are forced to operate in reactive way and particularly in the area of developing an information system without managers who are trained in information system management many failed the problem is as market changes companies need to deal with customers in more complex ways and their current information systems need to be updated without understand the architectural view or without an it strategy many just buy expensive equipment and add lot of hardware but receive no benefits because they not know how to integrate them into a cohesive system some add new components to their existing systems and hope to improve its performance while others buy new servers and more computers then find out that these things are not the solution whichever decision they made it is important to think strategically by understand the architect then design a system that can integrate various compatible components of information systems such as copy machines printers computers servers mobile devices video conferencing equipment etc into one cohesive system many companies have all the equipment but may not be using it effectively because they not have good information system managers thes technologies that could offer big benefits also could lead to big disasters in today's global economy it is the foundation for doing business and companies of all types are discovering that how they manage it is crucial to their competitiveness it determines whether the company's operation is efficient effective and timely whether employees have all information they need to their jobs this means that company owner and senior managers must define how the company will business in digital economy it means they must have good information system in place that span across all business units and it means they must resolve issues that business units cannot resolve such as what processes and what data will be standardized companywide unfortunately many company owners and top managers often not even know where to begin when it comes to managing information technology and they need someone who has this skill that is why
